# Server-side
<reply>
<data>
%repeat[120 x Testing large IMAP literal with custom FETCH. XXXXXXXXXXXXX%0d]%
</data>
<datacheck>
* 456 FETCH (BODY[TEXT] {7201}
%repeat[120 x Testing large IMAP literal with custom FETCH. XXXXXXXXXXXXX%0d]%
</datacheck>
</reply>

